go_data.justification: Mitochondrial complex I (NADH:ubiquinone oxidoreductase) catalyzes NADH oxidation in the mitochondrial matrix coupled to ubiquinone reduction.
NADH:ubiquinone oxidoreductase catalyzes NADH oxidation in the mitochondrial matrix.
Mitochondrial complex I is central to respiration and oxidative phosphorylation.
Mitochondrial complex I is central to oxidative phosphorylation.
